00:00:00.180 --> 00:00:04.710
Ushbu joylashuv tartibini yaratish uchun,
Men activ_main.xml faylini ochaman.

00:00:04.710 --> 00:00:07.670
Ushbu ko‘rinishni har birini vertikal 
ustunga qo‘yish uchun 

00:00:07.670 --> 00:00:09.340
menga vertikal chiziqli joylashuv kerak bo‘ladi.

00:00:09.340 --> 00:00:12.870
So‘ngra, avval nisbiy joylashuv 
tartibini chiziqli sxemaga o‘zgartiraman.

00:00:12.870 --> 00:00:17.110
Darhol, u ochilish yorlig‘i yopish yorlig‘iga mos 
kelmasligini ko‘rsatadigan xatoni ko‘rsatadi

00:00:17.110 --> 00:00:20.840
shuning uchun men nusxa ko‘chirib, 
shu yerga joylashtiraman.

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:22.100
Endi teglar mos keladi.

00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:23.930
Keyin, men ko‘rinishga qo‘sha olaman.

00:00:23.930 --> 00:00:25.720
Avvalo, menda miqdordagi matn ko‘rinishi bor.

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:29.880
Shuning uchun men ushbu matn ko‘rinishini ko‘rib chiqib,
matnni miqdorga o‘zgartiraman.

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.960
Keyin, nol deb ko‘rsatilgan matn ko‘rinishi boladi.

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:34.460
So‘ngra men birinchi matn ko‘rinishini nusxalashim 
va ostiga qo‘yaman.

00:00:34.460 --> 00:00:38.430
Men uni o‘zgartiraman, shuning uchun matn 
bu yerda ekran rasmiga mos kelishi uchun nolni ko‘rsatadi.

00:00:38.430 --> 00:00:41.500
Ushbu chiziqli joylashuv tartibdagi oxirgi tugma.

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:45.020
Biz ilgari joylashuv tartibimizga tugmani qo‘shmaganmiz, 
shuning uchun uni Google orqali qidiramiz.

00:00:45.020 --> 00:00:48.160
Agar siz brauzerni ochsangiz, 
androidni qidirib topishingiz mumkin.

00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:51.500
Ushbu birinchi havola yaxshi ko‘rinadi,
bu developer.android.com sayti.

00:00:52.570 --> 00:00:56.700
bu yerda tugma uchun hujjatlar,
matnning aksariyatini e’tiborsiz qoldirsak bo‘ladi.

00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:59.250
Sinflar umumiy ko‘rinishini 
o‘qish uchun pastga siljitamiz.

00:00:59.250 --> 00:01:03.000
U ozgina biz hali o‘rganmagan 
Java kodi haqida gapiradi, 

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.300
lekin pastda tugmacha uchun xml mavjud.

00:01:06.300 --> 00:01:09.280
Biz buni nusxalashimiz va 
kodimizda nima bajarishini ko‘rishimiz mumkin.

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:12.420
Bizning joylashuv tartibimizga 
ushbu ikkita matn ko‘rinishi ostiga tugmani qo‘shaman.

00:01:12.420 --> 00:01:16.030
Kodni shu yerdagi 
hujjatlarga joylamoqchiman. 

00:01:16.030 --> 00:01:18.900
Va endi satrni olib tashlash o‘rniga 

00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:22.280
men order tugmasidan foydalanaman.

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:24.900
Ushbu oxirgi qatorni o‘chirsak bo‘ladi, 
chunki unga ehtiyoj sezmaymiz.

00:01:24.900 --> 00:01:28.580
Ajoyib, endi siz nol 
ko‘rinishli miqdorga

00:01:28.580 --> 00:01:29.270
va buyurtma tugmachasiga egasiz.

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:32.220
Keling, nimaga o‘xshashini 
ko‘rish uchun 

00:01:32.220 --> 00:01:33.540
yashil tugma orqali 
ilovamizda ishga tushiramiz.

00:01:33.540 --> 00:01:36.290
Bu yerda uni hamon 
yaratilayotganini guvohi bo‘lamiz.

00:01:37.690 --> 00:01:38.660
Yo‘q, bu biz xohlagan narsa emas.

00:01:38.660 --> 00:01:43.470
Bizning chiziqli joylashuvimiz 
vertikal o‘rniga gorizontal holatda 

00:01:43.470 --> 00:01:47.586
Keling, biz orientatsiya atributini 
qo‘shganimizga ishonch hosil qilaylik.

00:01:47.586 --> 00:01:52.020
Android deb aytish uchun 
uni o‘zgartiramiz ; orientatsiya = "vertikal".

00:01:52.020 --> 00:01:53.570
Bu muammoni hal qilishi kerak.

00:01:53.570 --> 00:01:54.490
Keling, yana ishga tushirishga urunaylik.

00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:57.010
endi ancha yaxshiroq.

00:01:57.010 --> 00:02:00.270
Uch bola vertikal ustunda ko‘rinmoqda.

00:02:00.270 --> 00:02:01.810
Endi biz ushbu maydonlarni 
avvalda berilgan 

00:02:01.810 --> 00:02:04.160
skrinshotda ko‘rsatilganidek 
o‘zgartiramiz.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:08.460
Ekran rasmidan biz miqdordagi matn 
ko‘rinishi harf bilan boshlanganligini ko‘ramiz.

00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:13.950
Birinchi darsda biz android deb ataluvchi 
atribut haqida bilib oldik: textAllCaps ,

00:02:13.950 --> 00:02:16.230
va avtomatik tugallash holatidaligini ko‘rsatyapti.

00:02:16.230 --> 00:02:18.310
Agar u shunday ko‘rinsa, 
Enter tugmasini bossangiz 

00:02:18.310 --> 00:02:20.390
va u avtomatik ravishda 
siz uchun kod qo‘shadi.

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:24.970
Biz bu qiymatni chin deb belgiladik, 
chunki uni bosh harflarda bo‘lishini istaymiz.

00:02:24.970 --> 00:02:28.580
Ushbu atributni ishlatishga sabab 
matnni bosh harf bilan yozish 

00:02:28.580 --> 00:02:32.620
chunki agar biz qachondir UI ni 
o‘zgartirmoqchi bo‘lsak, natijada miqdor kamayadi

00:02:32.620 --> 00:02:35.650
masalan, ushbu matnni o‘zgartirish va 
almashtirish o‘rniga 

00:02:35.650 --> 00:02:38.020
atributni olib tashlashimiz kerak.

00:02:38.020 --> 00:02:41.840
Keyin, nol deb ko‘rsatilgan matn uchun 
biz 16sp hajmdagi matnni ishlatamiz.

00:02:41.840 --> 00:02:45.970
Hozir qo‘shib ko‘rganimizda avtomatik 
tugallash takliflarini ko‘rsatadi.

00:02:45.970 --> 00:02:50.000
men Enter tugmachasini bosib, 
qiymat uchun 16sp ni tanlayman.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.450
Shuningdek,uni qora shrift 
rangida bo‘lishini xohlaymiz.

00:02:52.450 --> 00:02:54.700
Men Android tizimining rangini 
qora rang uchun ishlataman,

00:02:54.700 --> 00:02:57.380
shunday deb yuritiladigan.

00:02:57.380 --> 00:03:00.558
Ajoyib, har ikki miqdor va nol ko‘rinishli
matnni ham nazardan qochirmaydi.

00:03:00.558 --> 00:03:05.011
Buyurtma tugmachasining holati yaxshi, 
chunki u avtomatik ravishda 
matnni bosh harfga aylantiradi,

00:03:05.011 --> 00:03:08.820
balandligi va kengligi ham 
shu tarkibga kiradi.

00:03:08.820 --> 00:03:11.898
Biz vertikal bo‘shliqni 
to‘ldirishimiz kerak.

00:03:11.898 --> 00:03:15.810
Miqdor va nol matnli ko‘rinishlar o‘rtasida 
16 dp li to‘ldirish 

00:03:15.810 --> 00:03:17.190
yoki chegara bo‘lishini xohlaymiz.

00:03:17.190 --> 00:03:20.027
Shuningdek, biz nol va buyurtma 
tugmachasi orasini 

00:03:20.027 --> 00:03:21.430
16dp qilamiz.

00:03:21.430 --> 00:03:23.960
Siz buni turli xil yo‘llar 
bilan amalga oshirishingiz mumkin,

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:27.650
men uni faqat ushbu tugma uchun joylashuvning 
yuqori chegarasi sifatida qo‘shaman.

00:03:31.410 --> 00:03:34.490
Va men ushbu miqdordagi matn ko‘rinishi 
uchun pastki qism sifatida qo‘shmoqchiman.

00:03:37.810 --> 00:03:40.810
Agar u bir xil ko‘rinsa, 
uni turli yo‘l bilan bajaring.

00:03:40.810 --> 00:03:44.000
Men pastki va yuqori chegarani 
tanlaganimning boisi

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:47.040
o‘rta maydon keyinchalik o‘zgarishini bilaman.

00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:49.670
Biz uni plyus va minus tugmachasi 
bilan miqdorni tanlash uchun o‘zgartiramiz

00:03:49.670 --> 00:03:54.620
va men hali ham miqdor sarlavhasi bilan 

00:03:54.620 --> 00:03:56.830
tanlagich o‘rtasida 16 pd 
bo‘sh joy qoldiraman.

00:03:56.830 --> 00:03:57.560
Tugma uchun ham shunday.

00:03:58.610 --> 00:04:01.280
Xo‘sh, endi uni qurilmamizda 
ishga tushiraylik.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:03.350
Ajoyib,biz xohlagandek ko‘rindi.

00:04:03.350 --> 00:04:07.150
Matn ko‘rinishi miqdori bosh harflarda,
nolinchi matn ko‘rinishida esa 

00:04:07.150 --> 00:04:11.710
qora shrift rangi, 16sp o‘lcham va
buyurtma tugmasi mavjud.

00:04:11.710 --> 00:04:14.540
Bizda ushbu ko‘rinishlar orasida 
ham 16dp bo‘sh joy mavjud

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:18.240
Juda yaxshi
Men deyarli unutdim.

00:04:18.240 --> 00:04:21.560
Quiz shuningdek ushbu tugmani 
bosganingizda nima bo‘lishini so‘raydi.

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:25.950
Xo‘sh, aslida u hech 
narsa qilmadi, hozircha.

00:04:25.950 --> 00:04:27.660
Keyin nima bo‘lishini bilish 
uchun kuzatishda davom eting.

